WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.624
Start on the exact operational screen for this guide.

00:00:02.624 --> 00:00:05.248
Open Booking Detail before approving a customer package.

00:00:05.248 --> 00:00:07.872
Review submitted agreement and insurance signals before approval.

00:00:07.872 --> 00:00:10.496
Verify identity, license, contact, vehicle, dates, and insurance against the booking.

00:00:10.496 --> 00:00:13.120
Open approval only after operational blockers are clear.

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:15.744
Do not approve if identity, agreement, insurance, vehicle availability, amount, or deposit risk is unclear.

00:00:15.744 --> 00:00:18.368
Open Review & approve after checking the submitted customer package.

00:00:18.368 --> 00:00:20.992
Set high-risk and deposit only when the customer package supports the decision.

00:00:20.992 --> 00:00:23.616
Approve and notify customer. This unlocks payment; it does not mark the booking paid.

00:00:23.616 --> 00:00:26.240
After approval, copy the payment link only after confirming the customer and booking code.
